YVDHOVE::System version 1.01
============================

This Perl module provides "System" functions for the YVDHOVE framework

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  IO::CaptureOutput

